Klub Polskiej Rady Biznesu.description: The Polish Business Roundtable Club (Klub PRB) is an elite private club housed in the historic Sobański Palace. Since the 1990s, it has been a top venue for Poland’s business leaders, featuring gourmet dining, salons, meeting rooms, and a garden terrace for discreet executive discussions.
